column2: Label
column3: Definition

column2: AL rdfs:label@en
column3: AL obo:IAO_0000115@en

column2: Phaleron paleopathology dataset
column3: Dataset created for the Phaleron Bioarchaeological Project that contains data about observations of pathological conditions in one specimen.

column2: Phaleron paleopathology dataset section
column3: Section of a paleopathology dataset created for the Phaleron Bioarchaeological Project containing data about one pathological lesion.
column5: There are several types of paleopathology dataset sections designed for specific types of observation.

column2: Bone addition dataset section
column3: Section of a paleopathology dataset containing data about one observation of added bone.

column2: Bone loss dataset section
column3: Section of a paleopathology dataset containing data about one observation of bone loss.

column2: Osteoarthritis and osteoporosis dataset section
column3: Section of a paleopathology dataset containing data about one observation of osteoarthritis and/or osteoporosis.

column2: Skeletal trauma dataset section
column3: Section of a paleopathology dataset containing data about one observation of skeletal trauma.

column2: Anatomical region of interest specification
column3: A dataset containing data about an anatomical region of interest and its usage in a certain research context.

column2: Phaleron anatomical region of interest specification
column3: An anatomical region of interest specification specifying aspect, anatomical site and extent of involvement for one anatomical region of interest that is part of an osteological observation.

column2: Phaleron anatomcial region of interest aspect specification
column3: An anatomical region of interest specification specifying the anatomical aspect of an anatomical region of interest that is part of an osteological observation.

column2: Comments on pathological observations
column3: A textual entity that is about a set of pathological observations.

column2: Skull pathology comments
column3: A textual entity that is about pathological observations on the skull.

column2: Vertebral column comments
column3: A textual entity that is about pathological observations on the vertebral column.

column2: Thorax comments
column3: A textual entity that is about pathological observations on the thorax.

column2: Os coxae pathology comments
column3: A textual entity that is about pathological observations on the os coxae.

column2: Shoulder girdle pathology comments
column3: A textual entity that is about pathological observations on the shoulder girdle.

column2: Upper limb pathology comments
column3: A textual entity that is about pathological observations on the upper limbs.

column2: Lower limb pathology comments
column3: A textual entity that is about pathological observations on the lower limbs.

column2: Mixed cranial bone formation and loss dataset section
column3: Section of a paleopathology dataset containing data about one observation of mixed bone formation and loss in the skull.

column2: Mixed postcranial bone formation and loss dataset section
column3: Section of a paleopathology dataset containing data about one observation of mixed bone formation and loss in the postcranium.

column2: Phaleron mixed bone formation and loss anatomical region of interest specification
column3: An anatomical region of interest specification specifying anatomical aspect and extent of involvement for various features that are part of an observation of mixed bone formation and loss.

column2: Vertebral pathology dataset section
column3: Section of a paleopathology dataset containing data about one observation of vertebral pathology.

column2: Skull size and shape dataset section
column3: Section of a paleopathology dataset containing data about one observation of abnormal size and/or shape in a skull.

column2: Long bone size and shape dataset section
column3: Section of a paleopathology dataset containing data about one observation of abnormal size and/or shape in a long bone.

column2: Phaleron regional anatomical region of interest specification
column3: An anatomical region of interest specification specifying a number of anatomical regions of interest within a certain skeletal region.

column2: Phaleron skull anatomical region of interest specification
column3: An anatomical region of interest specification specifying a set of anatomical regions of interest on a skull as defined by the Phaleron Bioarchaeological Project.
